This is a powerapp that is connected to a SharePoint list. I have built a SharePoint list with the following fields:
1. Title (Data type: Text)
2. Description (Data Type: Multiline Text)
3. DateTime (Data Type: DateTime with date and time selected explicitly)
4. Status (Data Type: Dropdown)
5. SpecialistName (Data Type: Text)
6. Comment (Data Type: Multiline Text)

